## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2584d-106">您必须对新<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A>项调用方法才能使创建成为永久创建。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2584d-106">You must call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A> method on the new entry to make the creation permanent.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2584d-107">调用此方法时，可以在新项上设置必需的属性值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2584d-107">When you call this method, you can then set mandatory property values on the new entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2584d-108">对于需要在调用<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A>方法之前设置的属性，每个提供程序都有不同的要求。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2584d-108">The providers each have different requirements for properties that need to be set before a call to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A> method is made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2584d-109">如果未满足这些要求，提供程序可能会引发异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2584d-109">If those requirements are not met, the provider might throw an exception.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2584d-110">请与您的提供商联系，以确定在提交更改之前必须设置哪些属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2584d-110">Check with your provider to determine which properties must be set before committing changes.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="2584d-111">下面的 Visual Basic .net 示例使用指定的<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>路径创建一个新的对象，然后在该容器中创建一个新项并将其保存。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2584d-111">The following Visual Basic .NET example creates a new <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> object with a specified path, then creates a new entry in the container and saves it.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Dim strPath As String = "IIS://localhost/W3SVC/1/Root"  
' Create a new 'DirectoryEntry' object with the given path.  
Dim myDE As New DirectoryEntry(strPath)  
Dim myEntries As DirectoryEntries = myDE.Children  
' Create a new entry 'Sample' in the container.  
Dim myDirectoryEntry As DirectoryEntry = myEntries.Add("CN=Sample", myDE.SchemaClassName)  
' Save changes of entry in the 'Active Directory Domain Services'.  
myDirectoryEntry.CommitChanges()  
Console.WriteLine(myDirectoryEntry.Name + " entry is created in container.")  
```  
  
